{"tid":1241951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罕見畫面！巨大獵人蛛捕食負鼠　狂叼猛拖驚悚「懸吊半空」","createTime":"2019-06-19T01:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T01:59:26.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f3c0a19064ebdb5b0c765ec79de12b41e95d793","tid":1241951,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:36:08.000Z","msg":"弱肉強食、適者生存，是大自然的定律，在動物世界中更是屢見不鮮。近日澳洲一對夫婦在旅行時，竟在旅館房間內看見一隻獵人蛛在獵食負鼠，直接叼著牠一路拖行，兩人立刻拿起手機將這驚悚的一幕拍下來上傳臉書，引發大批網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXnPczK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXnPczK.jpg&h=024e8ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，該起事件發生在澳洲，日前當地一對拉頓夫婦（Mr. and Justine Latton）到塔斯馬尼亞島費爾德山國家公園旅行，當他們回到旅館時，卻在房間內目睹一隻巴掌大的獵人蛛（Huntsman Spider）正在獵食一隻侏儒負鼠（Pygmy Possum），直接叼著長長尾巴的負鼠一路拖行，夫婦倆目睹這一幕當場嚇壞，立刻拿起手機將這毛骨悚然的畫面拍下來，隨後更上傳「塔斯馬尼亞的昆蟲與蜘蛛」（Tasmanian Insects and Spiders）臉書社團，引起大批網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CodreOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCodreOb.jpg&h=68d471f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對此，據報導指出，澳大利亞博物館（Australia Museum）蛛型動物理米利奇（Graham M<br />\nilledge）看完後為之震驚，驚呼「這真的很罕見，我第一次看到侏儒負鼠被當作獵物」，他表示，獵人蛛通常不會結蜘蛛網來獵食，而是透過快速的移動、銳利的尖牙和毒液來捕食獵物，經常是以小型鳥類、青蛙或壁虎為獵食對象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此，查爾斯達爾文大學（Charles Darwin University）生物保育教授沃納斯基（John<br />\nWoinarski）也表示，獵人蛛和東部侏儒負鼠的棲地非常不同，前者通常棲息在熱帶與亞熱帶的叢林，而後者則是棲息在高山等較寒冷的地區，因此牠們應該很難相遇，沒想到竟罕見同框，也意外引起許多野外及蜘蛛愛好者討論。"},{"pid":"65f4c1624e9d62f09e41f5f4025293061cb97cad","tid":1241951,"uid":7903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲就有圖"},{"pid":"042febc1f9293461a9420a016fc580a96e02af72","tid":1241951,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"又係澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b25f76aac1f2c5a36da4fef57c34ee41d32f59","tid":1241951,"uid":144064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562f74fa8c81419a7c3a878e2c3db55c485310c9","tid":1241951,"uid":20302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:39:51.000Z","msg":"大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452b285fc4874af1bd8bf1ca884bf05078f32154","tid":1241951,"uid":30604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"Everything In Australia Wants To Kill You"},{"pid":"d4aacb3cce3525357d3bca0d4ca9084dbe9da821","tid":1241951,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:46:18.000Z","msg":"依隻負鼠幾細隻<br />\n負鼠動作好慢 受驚會暈"},{"pid":"2130651e737b00f31b86bb9eb9543d965dc4c758","tid":1241951,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲就有圖"},{"pid":"6b4a10bf80316d4f6045ada56a2ba4aec7cbc1b7","tid":1241951,"uid":237555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:56:43.000Z","msg":"第二張圖<br />\n個獵人蛛個身好似人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32622eb1c68e3b1fbd6032846f3bbd6772b762be","tid":1241951,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:59:26.000Z","msg":"用毒蛛掟黑警有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}